data.description: Gorgeous 2 story home with just under 9 acres of land abundant with wildlife. This well maintained residence offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and tranquil countryside living. Step inside to discover an inviting interior flooded with natural light. The main level features a spacious living room, dining room, bathroom, laundry / mudroom, and kitchen. Upstairs you’ll find 3 bedrooms, one with a balcony overlooking the scenic backyard, a primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings and walk-in closet and 2 bathrooms. The basement has a large storage area plus additional unfinished living space, can easily add an additional bedroom and living room. Updates including new exterior paint, newer roof and gutters, newer HVAC, updated mudroom/laundry room/bathroom, updates to the kitchen, new lighting throughout the house, and more! Outside you’ll find a workshop with a woodburning stove. Just 15 minutes from Lincoln in the sought after Malcolm School District. Schedule your appointment today!
